import sys
import threading
def main():
    input = sys.stdin.readline
    t = int(input())
    for _ in range(t):

        a = list(map(int, input().split()))

                if need >= a[j]:
                    ans = min(ans, need - a[j])
            suf += a[j]
        print(ans)

if __name__ == "__main__":
